# The preview HMR-gate plugin is published to GitHub Packages under the
# @unseal-network org (see @unseal-network/vite-plugin-hmr-gate). Installing it
# needs a GitHub token with read:packages in the environment (CI / the E2B
# golden-template bake), e.g. //npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${GITHUB_TOKEN}.
@unseal-network:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com/
